          "id": "ver-2-1",
          "versionType": "ORIGINAL",
          "versionNumber": 1,
          "lyrics": "Yesu Kristu, Mwané ma Loba\nO bé na bwam bwa bésé\nO pula mba na nyo\nNa tombédi wé na lèm la mba\n\nO bé Nanga na mba\nO bé Loba na mba\nYesu Kristu, a bwam bwa mba",
          "annotations": []
        }
      ],
      "notes": []
    },
